<title>两年关店上万家，正新鸡排正被抛弃？</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E4%B8%A4%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%B3%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%87%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A3%E6%96%B0%E9%B8%A1%E6%8E%92%E6%AD%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%EF%BC%9F</link>
